HeidelbergCement Reports Higher Full-Year Net as Sales Gain

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-03-17T06:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/heidelbergcement-reports-higher-full-year-net-as-sales-gain.html
  HeidelbergCement AG (HEI)  full-year net
income rose to 511 million euros from 168 million euros, as
sales increased 5.8 percent, the company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in  Frankfurt  at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 